(33, 1, '2016-12-12 15:32:07', '2016-12-12 15:32:07', 'This category covers all 3D aircraft on our website. CG airplanes will fit into simulations, visualizations, advertisements and videos. Drone bodies and parts will delight fans of tiny flying vehicles. And the rigged models are ready to be imported into game engines. Flying games and simulators of both regular and VR type will find suitable 3D models.', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '33', '', '', '2017-01-08 17:31:10', '2017-01-08 17:31:10', '', 24, 'http://localhost:1240/?p=33', 3, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
