(27, 27, 'product_cat', 'The collection of 3D fauna - cats, horses, bears, rhinos, eagles, lions and more - can be found here. The CG 3D animals will satisfy the needs of advertisements or static scenes. We also have rigged animal models for games.', 24, 0),
